Package: demgenerator
Type: Package
Title: Simulates versions of the true DEM from the MERIT DEM for floodplains
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-01-15
Authors@R: person("Laurence", "Hawker", email = "laurence.hawker@bristol.ac.uk",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Laurence Hawker <laurence.hawker@bristol.ac.uk>
Description: Simulate plausible versions of a MERIT DEM for floodplains based on semi-variograms produced for several locations around the world.
    Alternatively, users can generate their own semi-variograms if ground truth data (usually LIDAR) is available.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
  raster,
  gstat
Suggests: rasterVis, RColorBrewer,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
